name: Chloe Grace Moretz
description:
This is a Lora of my Dreambooth checkpoint (https://civitai.com/models/1498/chloe-grace-moretz)

Dreambooth was made when LORA was not a thing yet and I did not believe that TI could produce life-like results.

Samples were made on the 1.5 base model, arcane diffusion, and on synthwave.

From now on I will be releasing new celebrities only as Loras (there is a backlog of already-made DBs which I am converting to Loras)

FYI: my technique of making new entries will not change - I will be making a dreambooth and then extracting it to Lora. (I will only upload Loras)
